{
  "stem": "16571.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was-- from what I've heard from my friends talking about what they went through, it looked like it was heaven, where I was in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because I was appointed to carry the food for the-- the youngsters who went to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was sort of small, but I was strong and muscly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I-- and I didn't go-- I never worked in Buchenwald, but I was taken out-- I was picked out to take the soup twice a day, in the morning and in the evening before they came home from work.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was like dust pans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we was bringing this food for the workers when they came home, or in the morning before they were all woken up to get ready for work, which was probably 6 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was lucky in that respect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we went by train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- just-- I don't exactly remember rightly how.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We was just taken by train to whole transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they picked out a few of us children, and we were bunked into Block 8, which was-- a lot of Russian children was in that block-- blockade.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As-- as-- as crowded as before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this time, we were-- we of course, obviously-- I forgot to mention that we were taken-- in Auschwitz we were taken to be deloused and shaved, and had to get in into a-- a vat.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow or other, when I got in in this room, I didn't see anybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw people going in, and I didn't see anybody else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought everybody jumps in there and they disappear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I got in this vat, and you had to sort of immerse in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
